<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>21 February · International Mother Language Day</title>
    <!-- Font Awesome 6 (free) for icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, system-ui, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f9f2e7 0%, #fff4e5 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            color: #2d2a24;
        }

        /* header with bengali and unesco touch */
        .header {
            background: #1b3b4f;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 30%, #235b6e 0%, #0a2e3f 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.8rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 20, 10, 0.3);
            border-bottom: 5px solid #e7b42c;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #1d5a6d;
        }

        .header h1 i {
            color: #f5c84e;
            margin-right: 12px;
        }

        .header .subhead {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            background: rgba(255,255,240,0.15);
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.3rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
        }

        .header .bengali {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans Bengali', 'Hind Siliguri', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        /* main container */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* intro card */
        .intro-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-radius: 40px 40px 40px 0;
            padding: 2.2rem 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 30px -10px rgba(98, 60, 20, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid #ffe6c0;
            border-left: 12px solid #c7493c;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #2c3a41;
        }

        .intro-text strong {
            color: #b13e2f;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .intro-text i {
            color: #1f6e8c;
        }

        .quote-box {
            margin-top: 1.8rem;
            background: #ebddd1;
            padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 100px 20px 100px 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            border: 2px dashed #ab6f51;
        }

        /* grid section (three pillars) */
        .grid-three {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .pillar {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px 10px 30px 10px;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.8rem;
            box-shadow: 10px 12px 0 #cdb89b;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            border: 1px solid #e2cfb5;
        }

        .pillar:hover {
            transform: translate(-4px, -4px);
            box-shadow: 14px 16px 0 #b59773;
        }

        .pillar-icon {
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            color: #bc4e3a;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .pillar h3 {
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #174e5c;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #f1cf9b;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .pillar p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #2f3d40;
        }

        .pillar .highlight {
            background: #fee9d6;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 0.2rem 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        /* language diversity map (visual) */
        .diversity-section {
            background: #274854;
            background: linear-gradient(112deg, #1f4a5b 0%, #12424f 100%);
            border-radius: 70px 10px 70px 10px;
            padding: 2.2rem 2rem;
            color: #fbf2e0;
            margin: 3rem 0 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: inset 0 -2px 10px #abc0c9, 0 15px 20px -10px #0b2b30;
        }

        .diversity-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-left: 10px solid #fccd7c;
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

        .language-cloud {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem 1.8rem;
        }

        .lang-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,235,0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
            padding: 0.5rem 1.3rem;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            border: 1px solid #eac48b;
            color: #ffefcf;
            transition: 0.15s;
            font-weight: 500;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #0f303b;
        }

        .lang-item:hover {
            background: #e1b87b;
            color: #102a32;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            border-color: white;
        }

        /* timeline / historic moment */
        .timeline-block {
            background: #fffbf2;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 2rem 2rem;
            margin: 3rem 0;
            border: 1px solid #f3d2af;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
        }

        .timeline-block::before {
            content: "২১ ফেব্রুয়ারি";
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 30px;
            background: #c7493c;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            padding: 0.2rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #0d4554;
            margin: 1.2rem 0 1.8rem 0;
        }

        .event-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .event-list li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding-left: 2rem;
            border-left: 5px solid #e7b42c;
        }

        .event-list li strong {
            color: #a33e2b;
        }

        .shaheed-minar {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            background: #eddac6;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #b4824a;
            color: #232323;
        }

        /* footer */
        .footer {
            background: #1b332b;
            color: #eee6d8;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 6px solid #d8a649;
        }

        .footer .footer-icons a {
            color: #ffda99;
            margin: 0 12px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .footer .footer-icons a:hover {
            color: #e9b44c;
        }

        .footer small {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        /* custom url display */
        .url-display {
            background: #1f2e30;
            color: #fad98b;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 60px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border: 2px solid #ecb554;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .url-display i {
            color: #f7bd49;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        /* responsive touches */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .header .bengali { font-size: 1.4rem; }
            .intro-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
            .quote-box { font-size: 1rem; }
        }

        /* fake bengali font fallback */
        .bengali {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans Bengali', 'Hind Siliguri', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <!-- custom url display: Bogura.crush.confo (no personal name) -->
        <div class="url-display">
            <i class="fas fa-map-pin"></i> Bogura.crush.confo 
        </div>
        <h1><i class="fas fa-globe-asia"></i> 21 February</h1>
        <div class="subhead">International Mother Language Day</div>
        <div class="bengali">আন্তর্জাতিক মাতৃভাষা দিবস</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem; background: #efb13b; color: #1a3038; display: inline-block; padding: 0.2rem 2rem; border-radius: 30px; font-weight: 600;">UNESCO · since 1999</div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- introduction section -->
        <div class="intro-card">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <i class="fas fa-quote-left" style="margin-right: 8px; color:#c7493c;"></i>
                <strong>International Mother Language Day</strong> is observed worldwide on <strong>21 February</strong> 
                to promote linguistic and cultural diversity and multilingualism. The date recalls the 1952 
                language movement in <i>Bangladesh</i> (then East Pakistan), where students in Dhaka sacrificed 
                their lives to protect their mother tongue <strong>Bengali</strong>.
                <i class="fas fa-quote-right" style="margin-left: 8px; color:#c7493c;"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="quote-box">
                <i class="fas fa-heart" style="color:#b3412c;"></i> 
                "Languages are the most powerful instruments of preserving and developing our tangible and intangible heritage."
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- three core pillars -->
        <div class="grid-three">
            <div class="pillar">
                <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div>
                <h3>heritage</h3>
                <p>Every language carries a unique worldview. 40% of the world's population lacks access to education in their own language. Protecting mother tongues safeguards ancestral wisdom.</p>
                <span class="highlight">7,000+ languages worldwide</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar">
                <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i></div>
                <h3>dignity</h3>
                <p>The right to speak, learn, and express in one’s mother language is a fundamental right. It empowers minorities and indigenous communities.</p>
                <span class="highlight">#MotherLanguageDay</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar">
                <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="fas fa-future"></i></div>
                <h3>future</h3>
                <p>Multilingual societies thrive. Technology and education in local languages unlock opportunities and preserve linguistic diversity for generations.</p>
                <span class="highlight">SDG · inclusion</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- language diversity visual -->
        <div class="diversity-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-language" style="margin-right: 15px;"></i> voices of the world</h2>
            <div class="language-cloud">
                <span class="lang-item">বাংলা (Bengali)</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Español</span>
                <span class="lang-item">中文</span>
                <span class="lang-item">हिन्दी</span>
                <span class="lang-item">العربية</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Português</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Русский</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Français</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Kiswahili</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Deutsch</span>
                <span class="lang-item">日本語</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Yorùbá</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Quechua</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Aymara</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Inuktitut</span>
                <span class="lang-item"> Māori</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Gaeilge</span>
                <span class="lang-item">isiZulu</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Bahasa</span>
                <span class="lang-item">नेपाली</span>
                <span class="lang-item">አማርኛ</span>
                <span class="lang-item">Soomaali</span>
            </div>
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; background: #2d5b6b; padding: 0.7rem; border-radius: 40px;">
                <i class="fas fa-microphone-alt"></i>  At least 43% of estimated 7000 languages are endangered.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- historical timeline (1952) and shahid minar -->
        <div class="timeline-block">
            <h3 class="timeline-title"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt" style="color:#c7493c;"></i> 1952 language movement</h3>
            <ul class="event-list">
                <li><strong>21 February 1952</strong> – Students at the University of Dhaka protest for Bengali to be a state language of Pakistan.</li>
                <li><strong>Salam, Barkat, Rafiq, Jabbar</strong> – several young men sacrificed their lives by police firing, becoming martyrs for their mother tongue.</li>
                <li><strong>1956</strong> – Bengali gains official status in Pakistan (later Bangladesh).</li>
                <li><strong>1999</strong> – UNESCO proclaims 21 February as International Mother Language Day.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="shaheed-minar">
                <i class="fas fa-monument" style="margin-right: 15px;"></i> শহীদ মিনার (Shaheed Minar) –  central monument in Dhaka, symbol of language rights.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- why it matters today (extra row) -->
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; align-items: center; background: #fff; border-radius: 80px 20px 80px 20px; padding: 2rem; border: 2px solid #f2c997;">
            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 200px;">
                <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher" style="font-size: 4rem; color: #1d6d7c;"></i>
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 5;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; color: #223d44;"> multilingual education matters</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem;">Learning in mother language boosts inclusion, literacy, and academic results. UNESCO calls for embracing linguistic diversity from early childhood.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- simple share / hashtag -->
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 3rem 0 1rem;">
            <span style="background: #174e5c; color: #ffd98c; padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 60px; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 10px 0 #0a2f3a;">
                #MotherLanguageDay
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- footer with Bogura.crush.confo inclusion (still no personal name) -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <!-- subtle url appearance again -->
            <div style="background: #243b3b; padding: 0.3rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 40px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #d8a649;">
                <i class="fas fa-link" style="color: #e9b44c;"></i> Bogura.crush.confo
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-heart" style="color: #f1b159;"></i>  multilingualism is humanity’s heritage</p>
            <div class="footer-icons">
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
            </div>
            <small>
                © 21 February — International Mother Language Day.  <br>
                Inspired by the spirit of 1952, Bangladesh & global linguistic diversity. 
                All voices welcome. — Bogura.crush.confo
            </small>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
